           SHORT="Kronolith is the Horde calendar application"
cat << EOF
The Kronolith calendar project currently provides a robust web-based calendar
for individual users with repeating events, and a smart algorithm to display
a whole day of events even if many of them overlap each other. Future plans
include support for shared calendars and merging multiple calendars into
a single view.
EOF
